attributes.description: The skies glimmer with mysterious purple vapors
Elves possess unparalleled quartz craftsmanship, through which they imbue their weapons with eternal sharpness
Elves whose kin have been exposed to the deep blue waters of the Sea of Liquidity bear a blue tinge
Light clothing, good for fast travel. Its red color is obtained from the leaves of Copium plants, commonly found on the Bearish Mountains
Long hair tied in a bun, to combat the heat of labour. Blue in color, often worn by scholarly individuals
Be wary of those who always have a story to tell
Elves are a naturally inquisitive lot, always doing their own research, skeptical of tall tales
Some elves are always suspicious of their surroundings, and can’t be fooled
Headwear is reserved for those with the means and desire to show off
The latest research and innovation allows the wearer to ascertain another’s power level
